Changes per file:
1. Rate limiting via rateLimitByIp() added at the top of each handler
2. Input sanitization via sanitize functions for emails, names, phones, UUIDs, strings
3. Structured logging via logger for errors, security events, and key actions
4. Replaced console.log/error with logger calls
5. All existing auth checks preserved
6. No business logic changed
